  <entry>
    <title>我写下虫子般蠕动的诗句</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/11/11/%E6%88%91%E5%86%99%E4%B8%8B%E8%99%AB%E5%AD%90%E8%88%AC%E8%A0%95%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%97%E5%8F%A5/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/11/11/%E6%88%91%E5%86%99%E4%B8%8B%E8%99%AB%E5%AD%90%E8%88%AC%E8%A0%95%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%97%E5%8F%A5/</id>
    <published>2022-11-10T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-12-14T08:56:27.090Z</updated>
    
    
      
      
        
        
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;那些虫子般的、蠕动的、鳞粉般的词语，&lt;br&gt;黏稠地在地下爬行，&lt;br&gt;惹得众人失声尖叫。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;它们如油脂般滑腻，&lt;br&gt;在脏兮兮的烛台上滴下。&lt;br&gt;如虫子般窸窣，&lt;br&gt;组成丰满、浓郁的诗句。&lt;br&gt;在堕落的躯体里，从喉咙里挣扎地涌出。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我随手翻开</summary>
        
      
    
    
    
