  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>湿漉漉的倾颓</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/11/11/%E6%B9%BF%E6%BC%89%E6%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BE%E9%A2%93/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/11/11/%E6%B9%BF%E6%BC%89%E6%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BE%E9%A2%93/</id>
    <published>2022-11-10T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-12-14T08:56:38.018Z</updated>
    
    
      
      
        
        
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;我终将被雨水淹没&lt;br&gt;身体和灵魂无一幸免&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;乌云在堆积、翻涌&lt;br&gt;像是一言不发的海浪&lt;br&gt;天空变得昏暗</summary>
        
      
    
    
    
